   GREETING-CARD _ WHISTLER,Canada _ Intent on ``getting lost in a
mountain of powder,'' staff photographer David Tulis journeyed
recently to Whistler-Blackcomb ski resort in British Columbia. This
full-page color photo essay captures the beauty, pleasure _ and
even warmth _ of a mountain of white. (Pousner, Atlanta
Journal-Constitution.)WITH PHOTOS.
</P>
