   GETAWAY-SEAST _ The first in a quarterly Getaway feature from
the Atlanta Journal-Constitution highlighting the Southeast Tourism
Society's ``Top 20 Events in the Southeast USA.'' This
Atlanta-based membership organization promotes and supports
regional tourism, including judging and publicizing the region's
top events. This package includes short stories on three of the top
winter fests, Kentucky Crafted in Lousiville, 2/5-6; Highland Maple
Festival in Monterey, Va., 3/11-12; Audubon Pilgrimage in St.
Francisville, La., 3/17-19; and a full winter festival listing.
(Townsend, Atlanta Journal-Constitution). 25. WITH PHOTOS.
</P>
