Jan. 14. The 6-year-old boy's rescue at sea triggered a diplomatic
tug-of-war between the United States and Cuba. Cuban-American
relatives in Miami threaten to file suit to block the return of the
boy to the island nation 90 miles south of Florida. By PATTY
REINERT.
