touring
</P>
<P>
   with Shawn Colvin and Jimmie Dale Gilmore. She even played three
</P>
<P>
   Southern Lilith Fair dates last year. Now, with the release of
her new
</P>
<P>
   album, ``Mile Marker,'' she's started her own record label and
hopes to be successful as an independent label executive, producer,
promoter and
</P>
<P>
   artist. By MICHAEL CLARK.
</P>
<P>
   FILM-HURRICANE (Los Angeles) _ In his new film, ``The
Hurricane,'' Denzel Washington hits hard as boxer Rubin
``Hurricane'' Carter, who was unjustly imprisoned for murder. But
the story turns out to be less about racism, injustice and
imprisonment than one man's spiritual journey. By BRUCE WESTBROOK.
</P>
<P>
