stars in
</P>
<P>
   ``Magnolia'' and ``End of the Affair,'' talks about the third
and fourth highly lauded films that she has seen released in recent
months. The movies open Friday, and her performances could land her
another Oscar nomination. By LOUIS B. PARKS.
</P>
<P>
   VIDEO-REVIEW (Undated) _ Reviews of films ``The Thomas Crown
