</P>
<P>
   and ``Don't Look Back,'' which are being released on videotape.
By BRUCE WESTBROOK.
</P>
<P>
   SELENA-BROADWAY (San Antonio) _ Two Texas women have been chosen
for the cast of ``Selena Forever,`` a Broadway-bound musical based
on the life of the slain Tejano superstar. The play is to premiere
