<HEADLINE>
&HT;     WHAT TO DO WITH A PRESIDENTIAL HAS-BEEN 
</HEADLINE>
   &HT;     (For use by New York Times News Service clients.)  
 &HT;     By MARIANNE MEANS  
 &HT;     c.2000 Hearst Newspapers  
<TEXT>
<P>
   WASHINGTON _ President Clinton, already fretting about how to
